# Paperwork Labs Brand Guide

## Brand Architecture

```
PAPERWORK LABS (Holding Company — paperworklabs.com)
  "We build tools that eliminate paperwork."
  │
  ├── CONSUMER BRANDS (free, own domains, own palettes)
  │   ├── FileFree ........... filefree.ai (free tax filing)
  │   ├── LaunchFree ......... launchfree.ai (free LLC formation)
  │   └── Trinkets ........... tools.filefree.ai (utility tools)
  │
  └── B2B BRAND (paid, one platform)
      └── Distill ............ distill.tax (compliance automation APIs + CPA SaaS)
          ├── Distill for CPAs (SaaS, $49-199/mo)
          ├── Distill Tax API (per-return)
          ├── Distill Formation API (per-filing)
          └── Distill Compliance API (per-action)
```

**Why this architecture**: Consumer brands are free and distinct — each owns a clear paperwork category. Distill unifies all B2B under one brand (Stripe model, not Intuit model). Paperwork Labs ties it all together as the infrastructure company.

## Brand Names

- **Company name**: Paperwork Labs (two words, both capitalized)
- **Legal entity**: Paperwork Labs LLC
- **Domain**: paperworklabs.com
- **Never**: PaperworkLabs, Paperwork labs, PAPERWORK LABS, PW Labs

### Product Names

- **FileFree** (one word, camelCase capital F's). Domain: filefree.ai. Never: File Free, Filefree, FILE FREE, File-Free, FileFree Tax
- **LaunchFree** (one word, L and F capitalized). Domain: launchfree.ai. Never: Launch Free, Launchfree, LAUNCHFREE
- **Distill** (one word, capital D). Domain: distill.tax. Never: DISTILL, distill (in brand context)
- **Trinkets** (one word, capital T). Domain: tools.filefree.ai

### Legal Footer (all products)

"Paperwork Labs LLC | California | FileFree, LaunchFree, Distill, and Trinkets are products of Paperwork Labs LLC"

## Logo Assets

**Status**: Logo assets pending for all products.

**FileFree**: Generate wordmark via Ideogram v3 (prompt: stylized "FileFree" wordmark, gradient violet-to-purple, dark background, modern sans-serif with distinctive lowercase "f" ligature). Generate monogram via Figma/Canva. Place in `apps/filefree/public/brand/`.

**LaunchFree**: Generate wordmark (teal-to-cyan gradient, dark background, modern sans-serif). Place in `apps/launchfree/public/brand/`.

**Distill**: Generate wordmark (deep blue-to-slate gradient, dark background, professional geometric sans-serif). Place in `apps/distill/public/brand/`.

**Paperwork Labs**: Generate wordmark (neutral zinc/slate, clean professional). Place in `apps/studio/public/brand/`.

### Logo Rules (all brands)

- Minimum clear space: half the height of the logo on all sides
- Never rotate, skew, add shadows, or place on busy backgrounds
- On dark backgrounds: use the wordmark as-is (white + gradient)
- On light backgrounds: use solid primary color for the full wordmark
- Never use gradients on light backgrounds — they lose contrast

